\begin_layout Theorem
(点到平面的距离) 如果有平面
\begin_inset Formula $Ax_{1}+By_{1}+Cz_{1}+D=0$
\end_inset

, 有点
\begin_inset Formula $P(x_{0},y_{0},z_{0}),$
\end_inset

那么有点到平面的距离
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
